## Auth

```bash
# .env (do not commit)
export SERVICE_COOKIE='paste full cookie from DevTools Network tab'
```

## Quickstart

```python
import os
from {{IMPORT_NAME}} import Client

client = Client(cookie=os.environ["SERVICE_COOKIE"])
chat = client.create_new_chat()
print(client.send_message("Hello!", chat["uuid"]))
```

Demo (offline, no cookie):

```python
from {{IMPORT_NAME}} import Client
c = Client(demo=True)
cid = c.create_new_chat()["uuid"]
print(c.send_message("hi", cid))
```

