## API

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `list_all_conversations()` | List chats |
| `create_new_chat(name="")` | New chat → `{"uuid"}` |
| `send_message(prompt, conversation_id, attachment=None)` | Send + get answer string |
| `chat_conversation_history(conversation_id)` | History JSON |
| `delete_conversation(conversation_id)` | Delete → bool |
| `rename_chat(title, conversation_id)` | Rename → bool |
| `reset_all()` | Delete all |

